PART 1: SPECTRAL CONCENTRATION → φ²
======================================================================

The Interval tournament Q-spectrum concentrates:
  Q_1 = m²(1 - O(1/p²)), Q_k << Q_1 for k ≥ 2

Spectral concentration ratio R = Q_1 / sum(Q_k):
  sum(Q_k) = m(m+1)/2 (constant for all circulant tournaments)

